about.summary: A unified framework for machine learning with time series

name: aeon
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "aeon" %}
{% set version = "0.5.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/aeon-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 857da4e0dd9244baed3de26a82c240c2eb74ae8fee7084596405c2d4685a6f88

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.8,<3.12
    - setuptools >61
    - toml
    - python-build
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.8,<3.12
    - attrs >=19.2.0
    - deprecated >=1.2.13
    - numba >=0.55
    - numpy >=1.21.0,<1.25.0
    - packaging >=20.0
    - pandas >=1.5.3,<2.1.0
    - scikit-learn >=1.0.0,<1.3.0
    - scipy >=1.2.0,<2.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - aeon
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://aeon-toolkit.org/
  dev_url: https://github.com/aeon-toolkit/
  summary: A unified framework for machine learning with time series
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - MatthewMiddlehurst
    - thewchan

about.summary: A unified framework for machine learning with time series
